unnormalised: Mhunnllear, mhaka title-anchi yaad aili dusrea disan, tumkam khobor asa? Khas korun medical shetrant. Tem ek vhodd vishay asa, barabor? Mhunnllear, tumi konnakui "Dr." mhunnunk xokona, kiteak tashi na? Mazi bhavachi bhurgi, Priya, ti Dr. Sharma zavnchea khatir khub mehnat korta.
normalised: Tor, hanv dusrea disa title-ancher vichar kortalo, tuka khobor asa? khas korun voizki shetran. tem thoddeshem voddlem vixoy, bara? toxem, tuvem konnakuy ek pornea monxak "Doctor" mhunn soddunk zainam, bara? mazyen bhai, Priya, ti Doctor Sharma zanchye khatir kitlem kam kortasa.

unnormalised: Mhaka sogllea vegllea title-ancher vichar korunk mell'lle. Tumchea basic Dr. koddlean suru koruya. Uprant MD sarke specialist astat, zo, mhaka sarkhem sanga zait, Doctor of Medicine mhunn asat. Ani uprant consultants-anchi puri duniea asa - Senior Consultant, ani Consultant Neurologist sarke. Tem ek ran zallear sarkhem!
normalised: Maka thoddeshem dusrea title-ancho vichar ailo. Amche kodden "Doctor" starters-ancho basic asa. uprant tuje kodden M-D sarke specialist asa, jem, maka sudhar, zarur asa, Doctor of Medicine asa. Ani uprant consultants-ancho ek vhodd sansar asa - Senior Consultant, ani Consultant Neurologist sarke. hem ek jungle asa!

unnormalised: Ani nursing staff-ak kiteak? Tumchea kodde RN asa, mhunnllear Registered Nurse, barabor? Ani uprant Nurse Practitioner (NP) ani dusrea sogllea torechea abbreviation ani title astat zaka hanv sarkhi ravpak prayatn korun harautam. Mazi bua, ti AIIMS-ant Head Nurse asa, ani tika-ui thodde sodunk poddttat!
normalised: Ani nursing staff-ancho kitem? tuje kodden R-N asa, tem Registered Nurse, bara? ani uprant Nurse Practitioner (N-P) ani dusrea sarki title ani abbreviation asa, jem hanv puros kori koryen harap zata. mazye bua, ti A-I-I-M-S ant Head Nurse asa, ani tika legit dusrea kitem puros korunk zai!

unnormalised: Uprant academic title astat. Mhunnllear, Prof. Gupta zannem mhaka college-ant biology shikovn dillem! To sodankal "Prof." mhunn mhunnunk agrah ditalo. Tem khub formal distalem, punn mhaka dista tannem tem kamaila. Ani PhD research-ant kam kortat tankam kiteak? Te rogeanchea upchar korunk nasleari te shetrant yogdan ditat.
normalised: Uprant academic title asa. Toxem, Professor Gupta, zanne maka college ant biology shikoile! To sodanch "Professor" mhunnonk sodtalo. Maka formal distalem, punn maka dista tannem tem kamaylam. Ani P-h-D-s research ant kam kortale? tim rogyank direct treat korchinakat, punn tim azunui shetranak maddat kortasa.

unnormalised: Ani sogllea vegllea areas of specialization-ancher mhaka suru korunk sango naka. Tumkam "Cardiologist," "Oncologist," "ENT specialist," ani sarke aikunk melltta, ani tem koxem konnui sarkhem ravpak xokta? Hanven ek favtt chukun eka dolleachea doctor-ak tvachechea rashevixim vicharlem! Khub lajek galla sarihi.
normalised: Ani mat korinakat sogllea dusrea area-nchi specialization-ancho vixoi-acher start korpak. tum "Cardiologist," "Oncologist," "E-N-T specialist," sarkhem aikta, ani te sarki asa, konkani tem sogllepuros korunk zata? hanv ek fautim chukun ek dollyachem doctorak skin rash vishean vixarlem! kitlench udas kortale.

unnormalised: Punn tem ruchichem asa, kitlen title-ank vhodd mahatv asta, khas korun hanga Bharata-nt. Mhunnllear, lok tumi khub hushar ani tumkam soglle khobor asa mhunn auttomatic-ki mandtat tumchea nanvak "Dr." mhunn asa mhunn. Zo, nischit rupan, sodankal nastach! Punn tem ek cultural vishay asa, tumkam khobor asa?
normalised: Punn hem interesting asa, kitlem vajan title vhavartat, khas korun hange Bharotan. Toxem, monis automatically assume kortat tum brilliant asa ani tuka sogllench khobor asa zar tuje title mureant "Doctor" asa. Jem, nitinachem sodanch aschem naka! punn tem cultural chitra asa, tuka khobor asa?

unnormalised: Konnank tori medical dunient title-ank sarkhem ravpak ek handy guide toyar korunk zata? Mhaka khobor asa mhaka eka guide-chi goroz asa. Atam, tumi mhaka maf korat, hanv ek cup chai pieunk vochot. Ta-ta atamchea khatir!
normalised: Anyways, voizki sansaranth title-ancher thoddi random musings. khoych konnak tem sogllen puros korche khatir handy guide toyar koronk zata? maka khobor asa hanv ek vaprunk zata. Ata, tum maka maf kor, hanv chaiacho ek cup piyonk veta. Ta-ta ata khatir!
